title: [Thurfel's Island]
description: The pier comes to a sudden and abrupt end with no guard rail or warning.  The broken and cracked bits of plank point to either storm damage or just plain rot.

The pier comes to a sudden and abrupt end with no guard rail or warning.  The broken and cracked bits of plank point to either storm damage or just plain rot.  A watery vortex churns dangerously in the waters just below the pier, its center crackling with energy.
